{"word":"αὐτάγρετος","slug":"αὐτάγρετος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n17545\" key=\"au)ta/gretos\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"suff\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">αὐτ-άγρετος</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ον</itype>, (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">ἀγρέω</etym>) poet. for <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">αὐθαίρετος,</foreign> <sense id=\"n17545.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">self-chosen, left to one's choice,</tr_> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">εἰ γάρ πως εἴη αὐτάγρετα πάντα βροτοῖσι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:16:148\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">16.148</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">σοὶ δ᾽ αὐτάγρετόν ἐστι δαήμεναι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0013.tlg004.perseus-grc1:474\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">h.Merc.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">474</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n17545.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">taken by one's own hands</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">exertions,</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0001.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:231\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.R.\">A.R.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.231</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n17545.2\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Act.\">Act.</a></gram></gramGrp>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">choosing freely,</tr_> <bibl n